# DESIGN.md — Sharmarke Hassan Portfolio

## Visual Theme & Atmosphere
Warm editorial minimalism. The portfolio treats itself like a well-edited 
long-form piece: generous white space, strong typographic hierarchy, one 
restrained accent colour. Nothing decorates; everything communicates. The 
tone is considered and direct — a PM who thinks before they speak and 
edits before they ship.

